extends layout

block content
  link(rel='stylesheet', href='/stylesheets/transcript.css')
  .main-container
    .progress-bar(style="width: calc(" + segment.number / segment.total + "* 100%);")
    .load-bar
    a.title(href="/about")
      img(src="/images/arrow_left.svg")
      h1.epnumber= "Episode " + episode.number || "No episodes found"
      h1.eptitle= episode.name || ""
    audio(controls='')
      source(src=audio type='audio/mpeg')
      | Your browser does not support the audio element.
    form(method='post')
      .formInput
        textarea(name="text" cols="55", rows="12", maxlength=1000 style="resize: none;")= segment.text
      .formInput.form-buttons.left
        a.button.secondary-button(href='/about') Exit
      .formInput.form-buttons.right
        input.button(type='submit', value='Submit')
    .instructions
      p Please just type the words you hear, even if there is more than one person talking. If you can manage punctuation, that's great, too. When you've corrected the text, click Submit and you'll get another sample. When you're done, click the exit button.